{"tid":2406659,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"伴侶有親密關係恐懼症","createTime":"2021-02-13T11:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T11:57:09.000Z","uid":41176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"79c0ab2036d3f86396957591882dbf2a953a67ad","tid":2406659,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"朋友拍拖有呢個煩惱<br />\n（我朋友唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n佢一直同女朋友相處都幾好<br />\n佢女朋友都一直表示好感激識到呢個男仔<br />\n但當佢想進一步（包括sex, 見家長, 同居等等唔同關係）嘅時候女朋友好多時都會拒絕或者表現出恐懼，或者想逃避呢個話題<br />\n有提過無原因地會怕太close同埋怕將來人生會好定型<br />\n但同時又表示我朋友想進一步嘅其實都係自己想要嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n我幫佢上網睇過呢類型伴侶有咩特徵<br />\n朋友睇完都話紅字有啲幾似<br />\n<br />\nFear of intimacy symptoms<br />\n<br />\nFear of intimacy may be obvious, but it can be misinterpreted as anger, indifference, or coldness. Someone who fears intimacy may:<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">have low self-esteem<br />\nhave trust issues</span><br />\nexperience episodes of anger<br />\n<span class=\"red\">actively avoid physical contact<br />\nhave trouble forming or committing to close relationships<br />\nhave a history of unstable relationships</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">be unable to share feelings or express emotion</span><br />\nhave insatiable sexual desire  （呢個佢話反而完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<span class=\"red\">live in self-imposed social isolation</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打另一半/自己經歷過呢個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇咩方法可以減輕佢女朋友嘅恐懼？<br />\n<br />\n我朋友真係唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f4e0e3c39d7aaa1aa9bf9316aaa0a771b5eea4","tid":2406659,"uid":258903,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T11:40:05.000Z","msg":"手都唔拖得<br />\n但有一日突然話佢有左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5b0e5c16776f2c37cf068cd0b